# --- Top-Level Protections ---
node_modules/
**/node_modules/

# --- Environment & Secrets (High Priority) ---
# Protects PostgreSQL credentials and API keys across all folders
.env
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
*.env
.envrc

# --- Build & Compilations ---
dist/
**/dist/
build/
**/build/
.next/
**/ .next/
out/
**/out/

# --- Database Specific ---
# Ignore Prisma generated clients if custom paths are used
**/generated/
# Ignore local SQLite files if used for development
*.db
*.db-journal

# --- Logs & Debugging ---
logs
*.log
**/logs
**/*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# --- IDE & System ---
.vscode/
**/.vscode/
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea/
**/.idea/
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
Thumbs.db